com.qtplaf.platform.task

Class TaskDownloadTicker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.qtplaf.library.task.TaskRunner
      • com.qtplaf.platform.task.TaskDownloadTicker
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Task, java.lang.Runnable

    public class TaskDownloadTicker
extends TaskRunner
    Task to download a ticker from a server, starting at the last data downloaded, up to the last data available in the server.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
